response.overview: Solid grooves and catchy songwriting have garnered underground metal band Jungle Rot a large base of dedicated fans around the world. Led by Dave Matrise on vocals and guitar, the Midwest-based quartet plays through a 14-song set list -- at full throttle -- in this explosive concert video. Tunes include "Fractured," "Misplaced Anger," "Lowlife," "Darkness Foretold," "Infectious" and "Scars of the Suffering."
response.title: Jungle Rot: Live in Germany
